<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Portfolio de Marc</title>
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" />
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Portfolio of Marc Plana, full-stack developer and computer engineering student."
    />
    <style>
      :root {
        --color1: #69B9FA;
        --color2: #7569FA;
        --color3: #698BFA;
        --color4: #69E6FA;
        --color5: #A569FA;
        --color6: #BCCBFA;
      }

      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background: var(--color6);
        color: #000000;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 2rem 1rem;
        min-height: 100vh;
      }

      main {
        max-width: 700px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        color: #000000;
      }

      .container {
        background: white;
        border-radius: 12px;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(105, 185, 250, 0.3);
        padding: 3rem 3rem 2rem 3rem;
        color: #000000;
      }

      .intro {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto 3rem auto;
        text-align: center;
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(20px);
        animation: fadeInUp 1s forwards;
        animation-delay: 0.3s;
      }

      .intro h1 {
        font-size: 3rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        color: var(--color1);
        font-weight: 700;
      }

      .intro p {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        font-weight: 400;
      }

      .projects {
        margin-top: 0;
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(20px);
        animation: fadeInUp 1s forwards;
        animation-delay: 0.6s;
      }

      .projects h2 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        color: var(--color1);
        text-align: center;
        font-weight: 700;
      }

      .project-list {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 1.5rem;
      }

      .project-list article {
        background: var(--color6);
        padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(105, 185, 250, 0.2);
        color: #000000;
      }

      .project-list h3 {
        margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 1.4rem;
      }

      .project-list p {
        margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem;
        font-size: 1rem;
        line-height: 1.4;
      }

      .project-list img {
        max-width: 100%;
        border-radius: 8px;
        margin: 1rem 0;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }

      .project-list a {
        display: inline-block;
        margin-top: 0.5rem;
        color: var(--color2);
        font-weight: 600;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      /* Margen entre enlaces seguidos */
      .project-list a + a {
        margin-left: 1rem;
      }

      .project-list a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
      }

      @keyframes fadeInUp {
        to {
          opacity: 1;
          transform: translateY(0);
        }
      }

      @media (max-width: 600px) {
        .container {
          padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
        }

        .intro h1 {
          font-size: 2.2rem;
        }

        .projects h2 {
          font-size: 2rem;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <main>
      <div class="container">
        <section class="intro">
          <h1>Hi, I'm Marc Plana</h1>
          <p>
            I'm a full-stack developer and computer engineering student
            passionate about AI, software development & data science.
          </p>
          <p>
            Welcome to my portfolio, where you can explore my projects, learn
            more about me, and get in touch.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="projects">
          <h2>Projects</h2>
          <div class="project-list">
            <article class="proyecto1">
              <h3>PATHFINDING ALGORITHM</h3>
              <p>
                This project implements a complete route planning system using
                pathfinding algorithms, with a web interface in React and a
                backend in Python (FLASK). It is designed to receive maps and
                coordinates dynamically and calculate the shortest path,
                integrating advanced logic such as track prioritization.
              </p>
              <img
                src="/pathfinding_demo.gif"
                alt="Pathfinding Algorithm Demo"
              />
              <a
                href="https://github.com/mplanav/PATHFINDING.git"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                >Pathfinding Algorithm Repository</a
              >
            </article>

            <article class="proyecto2">
              <h3>SWARVICE</h3>
              <p>
                This project is a web application that we developed with agile
                methodology with a backend in C++, data management in
                PostgreSQL, and a frontend with React.
              </p>
              <img src="/swarvice.png" alt="SWARVICE Screenshot" />
              <a
                href="https://github.com/AMEP-Serveis/React.git"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                >Frontend Repository</a
              >
              <a
                href="https://github.com/AMEP-Serveis/Final.git"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                >Backend Repository</a
              >
            </article>

            <article class="proyecto3">
              <h3>HEX GAME</h3>
              <p>
                A strategic board game implemented in JavaScript, featuring an
                intuitive UI and AI opponent.
              </p>
              <!-- Añade imagen y repositorio si los tienes -->
            </article>

            <article class="proyecto4">
              <h3>CONECTA 4</h3>
              <p>
                Classic Connect 4 game recreated using HTML, CSS, and vanilla
                JavaScript with responsive design.
              </p>
              <!-- Añade imagen y repositorio si los tienes -->
            </article>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
